{"id":303514,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-维权人士魏勤、王扣玛被羁押10个月后面临/","date":"2013-07-14T12:17:42Z","modified":"2013-07-14T12:17:42Z","title":"维权网 | 维权人士魏勤、王扣玛被羁押10个月后面临审判（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员王冬见报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>，上海维权人士魏勤、王扣玛分别被警方带走，被上海市公安局闸北分局以“涉嫌聚众扰乱公共场所秩序”罪刑事拘留，同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>被以“寻衅滋事”罪逮捕，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>案件已经移送到检察院，检察院曾于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span>两次退补侦查，闸北公安分局于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span>重新移送到检察院起诉。下周魏勤的代理律师尚宝军将前往上海开庭前会议，魏勤和王扣玛在被羁押近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>个月后将面临审判。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>魏勤因上访维权，多年来遭到数次行政拘留，上海世博会前夕被指“扰乱公共场所秩序”而劳教一年三个月。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海市闸北区检察院对魏勤和王扣玛的指控是，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，王扣玛以祭拜母亲为由，纠集魏勤等数十人在家中设灵堂、烧纸钱、喊口号。魏勤手举横幅，跟喊口号；警方另外指控魏勤，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，魏勤和数十人参加陈小明的祭奠，魏勤带头喊口号，其视频、照片被上传到互联网上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，上海市公安局静安分局指控，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，魏勤与王扣玛等人以祭奠王扣玛的母亲为由，在王扣玛的家中设灵堂、烧纸钱，并呼喊“还我人权，还我母亲，还我公道”的口号，造成严重的社会影响。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本月律师在会见魏勤时，魏勤表示自被关押后，从未收到过家人的片言只语，她非常担心年迈母亲的身体及儿子的生活，并希望能知道家人的现状。魏勤在看守所内坚强乐观，坚称自己无罪。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>魏勤多年来热心关注其他上访维权人士，魏勤被抓捕后，上海及各地维权人士多次为其呼吁并捐款，抗议上海当局对维权人士的打压，呼吁立即无罪释放魏勤等其他维权人士。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2002</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月，魏勤工作多年被工厂无故辞退，生活陷入困境。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2002</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月居住地又遭遇动迁（举世关注的东八块地段），</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>住房被非法强拆，从此走上充满血泪的上访之路。魏勤不但自己依法维权，还为其他权益受到侵犯的人维权，并成为零八宪章的首批签署人之一。因此遭到监控、行政拘留、劳教等迫害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sVnbrwKBYEg/UeJfVs4qxgI/AAAAAAAAlR4/BfJ209Z8RDE/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+285.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sVnbrwKBYEg/UeJfVs4qxgI/AAAAAAAAlR4/BfJ209Z8RDE/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+285.jpg\" width=\"235\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rhixT9B9Ph8/UeJfa4Hd7GI/AAAAAAAAlSM/aUM4oYBx4l4/s1600/%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587+286.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rhixT9B9Ph8/UeJfa4Hd7GI/AAAAAAAAlSM/aUM4oYBx4l4/s320/%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587+286.jpg\" width=\"216\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-wV-mlyJ2Boc/UeJfXK-Za4I/AAAAAAAAlSA/bjDWPu8R1-k/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+287.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-wV-mlyJ2Boc/UeJfXK-Za4I/AAAAAAAAlSA/bjDWPu8R1-k/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+287.jpg\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nmNzBiJ6ndE/UeJfbqp65XI/AAAAAAAAlSQ/Xt_AlVdNJbo/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+288.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nmNzBiJ6ndE/UeJfbqp65XI/AAAAAAAAlSQ/Xt_AlVdNJbo/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+288.jpg\" width=\"229\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-SfpYWC240Gw/UeJfi39NpAI/AAAAAAAAlSg/t_hwOggKMBo/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+289.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-SfpYWC240Gw/UeJfi39NpAI/AAAAAAAAlSg/t_hwOggKMBo/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+289.jpg\" width=\"223\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-oIdn7DIAG_k/UeJfdybVAyI/AAAAAAAAlSY/qme-ntohDck/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+290.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"228\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-oIdn7DIAG_k/UeJfdybVAyI/AAAAAAAAlSY/qme-ntohDck/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+290.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}